[h3 id=EffortInTasing 
	"Effort In TASing
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Even though I had TASed this games a few months ago, I wasn't satisfied with the outcome. Why? I was not able to control the RNG, as I have with the Machine Language (ML) games. After figuring some details out, with 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Maze-Mania|href=/8407S)
	", I decided to come back to this and apply my new understanding. This time, it wouldn't pay off...as any pre-loaded RND commands made the situation far worse. This was a rare situation, but the unmodified RNG ended up being the best solution here.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"If you would like to know more about the new method of RNG control, please visit the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Maze-Mania|href=/8407S)
	" submission for details.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Information about the operation of the RND command can be found via 
	[a href=https://www.c64-wiki.com/wiki/RND rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"here
	]a
	".
	$LF
]div
